      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered its whole life, always garaged, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for a ride that's basically flawless and ready for the road, you've found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
