    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. The S54 3.2L power plant remains the centerpiece, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline; both the VANOS system and rod bearings have been proactively serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, and the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission pairs seamlessly with the variable M differential lock for surgical power delivery. Every bushing and damper is in factory-spec condition, maintaining the precise suspension geometry and tactile feedback synonymous with this chassis. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
