      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem, and let me tell you, it\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom-level condition. It has been babied since day one\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells brand new! If you\u2019ve been searching for a car that\u2019s been cared for with total love and looks spotless inside and out, this is the one. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
